data.description: Discover Your Dream Cottage in North Park! This enchanting oasis, tucked away on a peaceful street, holds hidden treasures waiting to be unveiled. Step inside to find classic hardwood floors and a sun-drenched living and dining area. Ascend the kitchen staircase to reveal a versatile 600 sq ft walkout basement – your blank canvas for boundless creativity. Picture a wine cellar, a craftsman's retreat, a playroom, or endless storage possibilities! This home seamlessly melds vintage allure (hello, clawfoot bathtub) with modern luxuries like solar power, dual pane windows, and central A/C. The vast backyard beckons the potential for an ADU.
